# Portfolio listing automation

https://ymd-portfolio-site.pages.dev/ is the **personal portfolio** (Web works).

Store legal pages live on **personal-site** (separate).

## Agent must

- When a Web app gets a public URL: run `npm run register-app -- --name "..." --url "https://..."` **yourself**, then commit, push, and ensure Pages deploy (push to `master` or `gh workflow run "Deploy to Cloudflare Pages"`).
- Prefer also setting the GitHub repo **Website** field so daily `sync-apps` keeps picking it up.
- Never ask the user to run register/sync commands for listings.

## CI already does

- On push / daily cron: `npm run build` (`sync-apps.mjs`) then Cloudflare Pages deploy.
